By default webpage background will be in White in colour.
There are two ways to decorate your web page background:
1) HTML Background with colours.
2) HTML Background with Images.
Code = 
<body bgcolor="red+blue+black">
You can change text color:
code = <body text="red">
For Image you can give any image with the help of the path.
code =
<body background="Path with imagename and extension>
end
